    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my car and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved and taken care of. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend road trips! I\u2019m looking for a quick, easy sale, so I\u2019ve priced it to move. Come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019ll fall in love with how it handles!",
      "price": 29500.0,
