    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-performing car that has been treated with care. The exterior paint retains a beautiful gloss and deep reflection; while there are a few minor stone chips on the lower front bumper and a small superficial scratch near the rear wheel well, the body is straight and free of any major dings. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather seats are supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver's side bolster, and all original floor mats are included. Every button, switch, and digital display functions perfectly, including the heated seats and navigation system. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It has a comprehensive service history with documented oil changes every 5,000 miles. The engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains firm and quiet over bumps. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide confident stopping power with no pulsation. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for immediate use.",
